# Edge (Python 3.11) Conventions

The edge service runs on NVIDIA Jetson Orin Nano at each counter location. It pulls RTSP streams, runs YOLOv8 + ByteTrack, detects tripwire crossings, and publishes events via MQTT.

## Tooling
- Python 3.11+, type hints everywhere
- Poetry for dependency management
- Ruff for linting + formatting (no Black, no isort separately)
- mypy --strict
- pytest for tests
- Pydantic v2 for config and message validation
- asyncio for I/O concurrency

